  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>The hotel has an outdoor swimming pool and a state of the art fitness centre. A well located first class hotel for leisure or business travellers. (11/07SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is located in the city centre opposite Central World Plaza and within 10 minutes walking distance of Pratunam and Indra shopping areas. It is also 10 minutes walking distance from Siam Square.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Rooms are medium size and 28 square metres and tastefully decorated in pastels. Each room is equipped with a fully stocked mini-bar, PC connection, remote control cable TV with Asis video-text and in-house movies. A private fax and mobile phone can be provided upon request. Bathrooms are good, well-lit, and marbled.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is a cream-coloured rectangular modern high rise steel and concrete tower.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel has two restaurants in addition to a coffee shop. The Chinese and Italian restaurants are on the second floor. The coffee shop is at lobby level and has the ambience of a Parisian caf√©.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The lobby of the hotel has a distinctly European ambience. It is large with an attractive marble floor. On either side of the entrance are two lobby lounges that offer plenty of seating area.</Text>
  </Description>
